Source: Wardens of Iron, Northern Threat Assessment.

Thornwood is a necrotic estate-forest south of the Great Northern Forest canopy edge. Direct threat to Kowloon's southern trade lifeline. The Lantern Road passes through the forest. If Thornwood reaches the Road, overland commerce dies.

